description: Disassociates resources from a Firewall Manager resource set.

parameters.name: ResourceSetIdentifier
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the resource set, used in a request to refer to the resource set.

parameters.name: Items
parameters.description: The uniform resource identifiers (URI) of resources that should be disassociated from the resource set. The URIs must be Amazon Resource Names (ARNs). (string) ---

nested_items.name: ResourceSetIdentifier
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for the resource set, used in a request to refer to the resource set.

nested_items.name: FailedItems
nested_items.description: The resources that failed to disassociate from the resource set.

nested_items.name: URI
nested_items.description: The univeral resource indicator (URI) of the resource that failed.

nested_items.name: Reason
nested_items.description: The reason the resource's association could not be updated.
